# Optional hints for Podman local runs (copy values into .env as needed).
# Upstream: https://github.com/docker/genai-stack
#
# 1) Start Ollama on the host before compose (macOS / Windows typical flow):
#      ollama serve
#    Default compose URL is http://host.docker.internal:11434 — use compose.podman.yaml
#    so that resolves to the host under Podman.
#
# 2) If host-gateway does not work on your Podman build, set explicitly:
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://host.containers.internal:11434
#
# 3) To run Ollama in a container (Linux-style), use profile linux and:
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://llm:11434
#    Then: podman compose -f docker-compose.yml -f compose.podman.yaml --profile linux up --build -d
#
# LLM=llama2
# EMBEDDING_MODEL=sentence_transformer
